entries.title_d: A patrol of Rebel X-Wing fighters has interrupted your rescue operation. Dispatch them and carry on with the mission.
entries.title: Naboo System:  A Bump in the Road
entries.complete: \#pcontrast3 Imperial Station: < \#pcontrast1 You appear to be clear for the moment, continue on. \#pcontrast3 >
